Goal Description

Drive continuous service improvement and customer value creation by contributing to report design, SQL migration, delivery optimization, defect resolution, and process improvements. Proactively support successful customer delivery through technical ownership, client interaction, team coordination, and implementation of value-added technical solutions.

Success Criteria

• Prepare and contribute to monthly plans for Customer Value Propositions (CVA) for upcoming quarters.
• Deliver minimum 2 value propositions/CVA improvements per quarter through technical optimization, process improvement, automation, or quality enhancements.
• Ensure successful report design, development, migration, testing, and production deployment with minimal defects.
• Support on-time delivery, issue resolution, and proactive communication with stakeholders and clients.
• Improve delivery efficiency through technical guidance, reusable solutions, and process improvements.

Comments

Successfully contributed to customer value addition through BIRT report design, development, execution, and unit testing activities. Played a key role in MS SQL to Oracle SQL conversion and migration activities to improve compatibility and delivery effectiveness. Actively participated in client discussions, status meetings, technical clarifications, and prompt issue resolution. Coordinated with team members to track deliverables and ensure successful report installation, production deployment, and defect-free delivery. Supported QC defect fixes, production data validation, and proactive communication to ensure customer satisfaction and on-time delivery.
